Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties

Class TranslationDetail

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.TranslationDetail
public class TranslationDetail extends Object
TranslationDetail provides translated strings for an open metadata element for a specific language/locale.
